<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Verify Your Email</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Welcome to Brainiac LMS!</h1>
    <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
    <p>Thank you for registering with Brainiac LMS. Please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
    <a href="{{url}}" class="button">Verify Email</a>
    <p>If you didn't create an account with us, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    <p>This verification link will expire in 24 hours.</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br>The Brainiac Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>